---
title: "bridgeAssets (FeeAggregator)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_receiver: check allowlisted receiver
    q_check_receiver --> q_error_receiver: !allowlisted(chainSelector, receiver)
    q_error_receiver --> [*]: revert ReceiverNotAllowlisted
    q_check_receiver --> q_check_empty: receiver allowlisted
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: bridgeAssetAmounts.length == 0
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_build_msg: length > 0
    q_build_msg --> q_get_fee: _buildBridgeAssetsMessage(amounts, receiver, extraArgs)
    q_get_fee --> q_check_bal: fees = ccipRouter.getFee(chainSelector, message)
    q_check_bal --> q_error_bal: fees > linkBalance
    q_error_bal --> [*]: revert InsufficientBalance
    q_check_bal --> q_approve_link: fees <= linkBalance
    q_approve_link --> q_send: safeIncreaseAllowance(ccipRouter, fees)
    q_send --> [*]: messageId = ccipRouter.ccipSend(chainSelector, message)

    note right of q_build_msg
        INV-001: Only allowlisted receivers on allowlisted chains can receive bridged assets
        INV-002: Only allowlisted assets can be bridged
        INV-003: LINK balance must cover bridging fees
        INV-004: Caller must have BRIDGER_ROLE
    end note
